Name: Antivirus.exe
Rules: On play, remove virus

Name: CPU Clock
Rules: On turn, Fetch tick card

Name: Browser
Rules: Each turn, you must move a virus card from the discard to the deck and shuffle.

Name: Task Manager
Rules: On turn, steal program, virus if none

Name: Encryption
Rules: While you have this card, your cards cannot be stolen or transferred.

Name: Bad Link!
Rules: On play, lose two cards. You may choose to add this

Name: Power Outage!
Rules: Tick cards can't be played, can't win

Name: Misplaced Juice!
Rules: Discard hand, this card cannot be stolen or transferred.

Name: Full Memory!
Rules: Your hand limit is 4

Name: Data Mining
Rules: The next player draws from the top of the discard.

Name: Timely Draw
Rules: Draw equal to timers played

Name: Disk Cleanup
Rules: Everyone discards down to 5 cards

Name: Quit
Rules: Discard any command, program, or virus card

Name: Force Exit
Rules: You may move up to two program or virus cards between players

Name: Screen Sharing
Rules: Move any two cards from player to player

Name: Networking
Rules: Gather all programs and virus, shuffle, redistribute equally

Name: December '69
Rules: Discard all tick cards in play, draw and discard until tick card comes up

Name: Suite Deal
Rules: If you have 7 or more programs in play

Name: Advanced User
Rules: If you have Registry and Task Manager

Name: Off, Then On
Rules: If you loose all cards in your hand then draw again

Name: A Millenial's Touch
Rules: If you have two of Werd Editor, Browser, Full Memory!

Name: Glass Half Full
Rules: If you have Misplaced Juice! and Full Memory!

Name: Befriend a Prince
Rules: If you have Bad Link! and Antivirus.exe or Browser

Name: Faster, Hotter, Better
Rules: If you have Overclocked, any program and GPU Accelerated is in play

Name: Upgrade
Rules: If you have three viruses or more

Name: Firewall
Rules: If you have three viruses or more and Antivirus.exe

Name: A Regular Hacker
Rules: If there are six commands in play and you add a seventh

Name: App Store 4
Rules: Draw 4 cards per turn

Name: App Store 3
Rules: Draw 3 cards per turn

Name: Multitasking 3
Rules: Play 3 cards per turn

Name: Multitasking 2
Rules: Play 2 cards per turn

Name: Child's Play
Rules: All scripts and ends that are drawn must be played

Name: Recycle Bin
Rules: Discard two cards to draw from the top of the discard

Name: Bytes and Pieces
Rules: Draw 8 cards, then give a card to each player from your hand

Name: Just a Nibble
Rules: All players' hand limit is 4.

Name: Stock Wares
Rules: All players' are allowed up to 4 programs and viruses.

Name: Quarantine
Rules: Discard two cards to move a virus from player to player

Name: Copy/Paste
Rules: Make a copy of a card, and give it to another player

Name: Overclocked
Rules: Draw an additional card for each timer in play

Name: GPU Accelerated
Rules: Draw an additional card for each program you have, discard an additional card for each virus you have.

Name: Ask Your Grandson
Rules: You may let a player steal a random card from your hand to draw two cards

Name: Clear Command Line
Rules: Discard all active command, play, and draw cards, including this one.

Name: Public Network
Rules: Play with hands open
